media:group.media:title: How Disc Brakes Works - Part 2 | Autotechlabs
media:group.media:description:
AutoTechLabs proudly presents the second part of the presentation  "How disc brakes works".The presentation defines the working of the brake master cylinder and brake boosters(Servo) and also explains how the force you applied on the brake pedal is transferred to the brake calipers. If you missed the first part, we recommend you to watch the first part before this presentation.
